            <title>[FLINK-942] Config key &quot;env.java.opts&quot; does not effect JVM args</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-942</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Setting custom args for the JVM as in &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;env.java.opts: -Dio.netty.leakDetectionLevel=paranoid
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;has no effect for the started JVMs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A fix is coming up.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
